title: Ebro In The Morning - Kanye Out Of Coachella + Strange Snacks and Cereals
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 4/5/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the fact that DJ John doesn't know what Chex are, the rebranding of tangerines to clementines, and Kanye dropping out of Coachella.  

Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems and get the latest news with Flashing Lights. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
